com.argox.sdk.barcodeprinter.util

Class LogFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.argox.sdk.barcodeprinter.util.LogFile

  • public final class LogFile
extends java.lang.Object
    The class provides static methods to log all the activities of related functions of this class library in specified files. Only if the log file exists, and enabled = 'true', then information about all functions in this class library will be logged.
